::Inu-Yasha::

Inu-Yasha unwraps and looks in the area for Koj as he plays part of a 
transmission. "2 units under attack ....swamps."

::Koj::

Koj breaks his Focus. "Damn Inu-Yasha you go help out fly low past the 
maximal base pull the autogun fire and I'll slip in."

::Inu-Yasha::

"Feh" As he spreads his wing he takes off Flying low and close to the 
maximal base trying to draw all the autogun fire he can. Taking some hits to 
his side damageing his armor.

::Koj::

Koj focusing on blending in runs for the open bay doors and tries slip in.

::Inu-Yasha::

Inu-Yasha sees Koj getting close to the doors and take off towards the 
swamp.
